pageContext.claim: “Getting ready to land in Louisiana to do Rally with Great Republican @EddieRispone for Governor. He will get your taxes and auto insurance (highest in Country!) way down.”
pageContext.analysis: For six years straight, Michigan has had the highest car insurance rates, according to insure.com. Louisiana has the second highest: "A high number of uninsured drivers combined with less than stellar weather and high population density led these states onto the most expensive states for car insurance list."
